1. Download ie: 'https://github.com/MediaFrontPage/mediafrontpage'
2. Copy all files to the web server directory eg /var/www/ 
3. Cmod 777 all files including the root folder.
4. Install 'php5-curl'

NOTE
All settings are maintained in Media Front Page under settings

OPTIONAL
Create a folder named 'sbpcache' and allow write access (for caching sickbeard posters)